node.text:
#KTMBlog - The KTM 250 SX-F you can buy at your local dealer is remarkably similar to the machine raced by Tom Vialle to victory in the 2020 MX2 World Championship. The Red Bull KTM Factory Racing bikes used by Vialle, Hofer, and Guadagnini do of course boast a selection of upgrades in order to race at the highest level of motocross.

We take a look at the different changes and performance parts in the latest edition of the KTM BLOG - check it out, link in bio!

#KTM #ReadyToRace #Motocross #MXGP #RaceOrange #KTMOffroad #KTM250SXF

node.text:
#KTMPowerWear - Sporty, stylish, and packed with safety features, the RESONANCE LEATHER JACKET is the perfect choice for KTM DUKE riders looking to stay casual and protected.

Made from premium 1.3mm cowhide, the jacket boasts removable pads in the shoulders and elbows, space for a back protector, and displays subtle KTM and Alpinestars branding to finish off the look!

#KTM #ReadyToRace #WornWithIntent

node.text:
Fuelled up, prepped, and READY TO RACE!

The KTM 450 SX-F needs no introduction - it boasts a championship-winning pedigree and class-leading performance. When the gate drops, it is THE machine to beat!

#KTM #ReadyToRace #RaceOrange #KTM450SXF

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by KTM on July 27, 2021. May be an image of motorcycle.

node.text:
Fast on track and fast to sell out! It took just four minutes and 32 seconds for all 100 of our hyper-focused KTM RC 8C machines to be snapped up by excited buyers, with 25 of them opting to pick up their machines at an exclusive handover event in Jerez where they will be able to ride alongside Red Bull KTM Factory Racing test riders Dani Pedrosa and Mika Kallio.

If you still want to get your hands on one of the exclusive track-focused bikes, we have created an online waiting list to give you a second chance. Click the link in bio to find out more.

#KTM #ReadyToRace #KTMRC8C #RaceRC

#KTMPowerParts - An absolute must for any KTM 1290 SUPER DUKE R owner, the FACTORY FOOTPEG SYSTEM is a work of high-performance art! CNC-milled from aluminum, with carbon heel plates, the adjustable footpegs allow increased ground clearance, a sportier riding position, and deliver a real factory race look.

Click the link in bio to find out more!

#KTM #ReadyToRace #IntensifyYourRide

node.text:

Packed with a selection of KTM PowerParts, and a unique graphics kit to commemorate the iconic event, the limited-edition machine is ready to face all conditions and the toughest terrain.

#KTM #ReadyToRace #KTM300EXCTPI #Erzbergrodeo #RaceOrange #KTMOffroad

node.text:
#KTMPowerWear - For the true orange bleeder, the J-6 AIR SHOES are high-quality, sneaker-styled riding boots designed to protect your ankles and feet while delivering a more casusal style.

With an outer made from full-grain leather and suede, and added heel, toe, and mid sole protection, the boots look great while keeping you safe.

For more info, click the link in bio.
